org.openmodelica.simulation.core.init_txt_handling
Class InitTXT

java.lang.Object
  org.openmodelica.simulation.core.init_txt_handling.InitTXT

public class InitTXT
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents an OpenModelica init.txt file structure which will be used while reading and manipulating an init.txt file. This file is generated by the OMC and is used by OpenModelica to initialize a corresponding simulation runtime executable.

Author:
EADS Innovation Works, Parham Vasaiely, Parham.Vasaiely@gmx.de
